---
title: California Turkey Sammies with Smashed Avocado
description: Quick, easy and flavourful are the best ways to describe these California-inspired sandwiches stacked with smashed avocado, pickled shallots and juicy, BBQ-spiced turkey! We'd say this is a winning turkey dinner!
